title: Various Artists - Caferino Albuquerque Vol. 6 [trip-hop]
description:
What waits you in the sixth volume of Caferino Albuquerque? Not much, at least not as much as what awaits in Vol. 7. For the moment, another satisfying chunk of awesome, more or less obscure trip-hop tunes.
Enjoy! :)
